                  <div style={{ fontSize: '13px', fontWeight: 700, color: gold, marginBottom: '16px', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: '6px' }}>
                    🏆 2024 Pi Commerce Hackathon Winner — Pi Network v1.8
